'From Squeak3.2alpha of 8 October 2001 [latest update: #4418] on 16 October 2001 at 4:22:10 pm'!"Change Set:		Modules-2Date:			6 September 2001Author:			Henrik GedenrydInstall sensitive methods that rely on others already being in place."!!Behavior methodsFor: 'testing method dictionary' stamp: 'hg 8/30/2001 18:43'!scopeHas: name ifTrue: assocBlock 	"If the argument name is a variable known to the receiver, then evaluate 	the second argument, assocBlock."	| assoc |	(assoc _ Smalltalk associationAt: name ifAbsent: []) == nil		ifFalse: [assocBlock value: assoc.				^ true].	^false! !!Class methodsFor: 'compiling' stamp: 'hg 10/1/2001 20:40'!scopeHas: varName ifTrue: assocBlock	^self lenientScopeHas: varName ifTrue: assocBlock! !!Class methodsFor: 'organization' stamp: 'hg 9/30/2001 16:27'!module 	^module ifNil: [Module smalltalk]! !!Class methodsFor: 'organization'!module: mod	module _ mod! !"Postscript:Run the code to initially convert the image to modules."Module convertSystemOrganizationToModules.FromVersion0p0000to0001 run!